<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="together-adv">together <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tə'ɡeðə(r)/    美 /tə'ɡeðər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>共同；一起：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>travel together 
一起旅行</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="together-with">together with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>和：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My friend Ann, together with me, is going to do field study. 
我的朋友安要和我一起去野外考察。</p><footer>2012 重庆改</footer></div>

<p>注: 句子的谓语动词应该与together with前面的主语保持人称与数的一致。  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Dr Smith, together with his wife and daughters, <strong><em>_</em></strong> (be) going to visit Beijing this summer.
  （2009 陕西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. is  </p></div>